1
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:25,040
LAST WEEK TONIGHT
WITH JOHN OLIVER

2
00:00:25,160 --> 00:00:27,160
Season II, episode 2

3
00:00:28,880 --> 00:00:34,000
Welcome to Last Week Tonight.
I'm John Oliver.

4
00:00:34,400 --> 00:00:39,960
Thank you for being with us.
A quick recap of this week.

5
00:00:40,040 --> 00:00:42,840
We begin tonight in Yemen.

6
00:00:43,240 --> 00:00:48,400
Home to 26 million Yemeni people
and 27 million American drones.

7
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:53,960
For years Yemen has worked closely
with the US on counterterrorism issues.

8
00:00:54,120 --> 00:00:58,320
Their government collapsed recently.
This week, things got even worse.

9
00:00:58,760 --> 00:01:01,960
The United States closing down
its embassy in Yemen.

10
00:01:02,080 --> 00:01:05,920
The State Department evacuated
dozens of diplomatic officials,

11
00:01:06,040 --> 00:01:10,080
urging all Americans
to leave that country immediately.

12
00:01:10,720 --> 00:01:15,560
Yes, if you are an American
diplomat in Yemen, evacuate.

13
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:17,720
If you're an American tourist,

14
00:01:17,840 --> 00:01:21,200
what the fuck were you doing
taking a vacation in Yemen ?

15
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,720
Bad choice.

16
00:01:23,960 --> 00:01:28,000
A rebel group called the Houthis
appears to be in charge in Yemen.

17
00:01:28,120 --> 00:01:30,800
So, who are they ?
And can we work with them ?

18
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:34,680
When you speak to them,
they're quite polite and pleasant.

19
00:01:34,960 --> 00:01:39,640
Lovely. How lovely.
Rebels who are polite and pleasant.

20
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:41,280
Y'know, like Drake.

21
00:01:43,000 --> 00:01:45,400
This all sounds
like it's tremendous news,

22
00:01:45,480 --> 00:01:48,000
unless I interrupted you
too early.

23
00:01:48,440 --> 00:01:51,640
They're polite and pleasant,
but one of their slogans is:

24
00:01:51,720 --> 00:01:52,800
death to America.

25
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:56,640
Okay then, okay.
That is completely unacceptable.

26
00:01:56,840 --> 00:02:00,200
Unless they're referring
to the '70s soft rock band America.

27
00:02:00,400 --> 00:02:02,480
In which case
I totally support them.

28
00:02:03,320 --> 00:02:06,280
You've been through a desert
on a horse with no name ?

29
00:02:06,360 --> 00:02:10,040
Did it ever occur to you
it's your job to name the horse ?

30
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:12,320
Call it Cinnamon and ride back.

31
00:02:14,240 --> 00:02:18,080
You might notice he said,
one of their slogans.

32
00:02:18,160 --> 00:02:20,480
And that's because
the full slogan reads:

33
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:24,200
"God is great, death to America,
death to Israel, curse the Jews,"

34
00:02:24,280 --> 00:02:26,640
"victory to Islam",
which is horrifying,

35
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:30,240
but still slightly less odious
than "I'm Lovin' it."

36
00:02:31,440 --> 00:02:34,560
Also there is some
potentially good news here:

37
00:02:34,680 --> 00:02:37,600
not only are the Houthis
against Al Qaeda.

38
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:40,160
They may be trying
to moderate their tone.

39
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:44,720
I interviewed their leader here
and he was very adamant

40
00:02:44,800 --> 00:02:47,560
about trying to have
better relations with the US

41
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:50,560
and he even went so far
as to repudiate their slogan

42
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:54,680
and say "that's just a slogan,
we don't mean it literally."

43
00:02:55,280 --> 00:03:00,360
Okay then. At this point the phrase
death to America lost its meaning.

44
00:03:01,000 --> 00:03:03,560
It's like,
we should really hang out sometime

45
00:03:03,640 --> 00:03:07,040
or I'm sorry, or I love you,
they're things to say...

46
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,360
Moving on to other major news
this week,

47
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:13,640
