scintillating dialogue such as this ?

53
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:38,000
That's impressive.
You a girl scout ?

54
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:44,920
No, organized group activities
aren't really my thing.

55
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:51,360
