key selling point.

147
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:10,040
You get basketball, football,
tennis, golf and...

148
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:12,000
And the famous swimsuit issue.

149
00:10:12,080 --> 00:10:16,400
Revealing 1991 swimsuit issue
and the free sneaker phone.

150
00:10:16,560 --> 00:10:19,400
- The swimsuit issue.
- That's the icing on the cake.

151
00:10:20,280 --> 00:10:22,720
The swimsuit issue
is still moving copies.

152
00:10:22,800 --> 00:10:26,960
It sold more than 800 000 copies
on newsstands in 2013,

153
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:31,600
more than 10 times what a regular
issue of Sports Illustrated sold.

154
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:36,120
