of any tobacco goods.

322
00:21:29,520 --> 00:21:34,080
Zero trade ! Zero.
Ukraine is inserting themselves

323
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:36,640
into something
they have nothing to do with.

324
00:21:36,720 --> 00:21:40,520
They take the Kanye West approach
to international trade disputes.

325
00:21:40,840 --> 00:21:43,720
Just wiggling in there.

326
00:21:44,760 --> 00:21:49,760
The truth is, tobacco companies
have encouraged these suits,

327
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:52,360
