of international trade litigation,

380
00:25:13,800 --> 00:25:17,000
suggesting Togo would lose
any legal challenge by citing

381
00:25:17,080 --> 00:25:20,600
an Australian high court decision,
which they write:

382
00:25:20,840 --> 00:25:25,560
