a privation of property rights."

383
00:25:25,760 --> 00:25:29,120
The court case they're referring to
is the one from earlier.

384
00:25:29,240 --> 00:25:33,000
The one tobacco companies
lost so badly,

385
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:35,120
